arts.ttl: Arsenal 1-0 Fulham: Substance Over Style as Arsenal Go Back To The Top of the Table
arts.sum: Fulham were compact, disciplined, and clever in the use of the ball, forcing their fellow Londoners to sweat in the first half and at the start of the second. Declan Rice and Martin Zubimendi completed the midfield unit, Leandro Trossard started over Gabriel Martinelli on the left wing, and Riccardo Calafiori continued as the first-choice left back over Myles Lewis-Skelly .
